data.description: $5000 in closing costs with preferred lender! This gem is located in a quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Central Texas! An allergen-friendly home greets as you open the door with no carpet throughout this abode. The environment is perfectly set for a gathering of any size in this open-Floorplan setting. Your kitchen and bathroom counters are beautifully adorned with granite countertops adding a stylish and durable touch! Keep cool on warm summer days with your newly installed AC. Enjoy nights in front of the fireplace or relaxing days out on the expansive covered patio.  As an added bonus, the garage is set up for  multi- use with epoxy floors and insulation! Located a short 12 minute drive to Fort Cavazos and 50 minutes from the largest indoor water park in the country, 4703 Poppywood awaits your presence…
